00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 10=

4
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:15,990
Be careful, Young Master.

5
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:17,560
Who's there?

6
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,359
There's no one?

7
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,079
Could it be a wild cat?

8
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:31,159
There's firelight.

9
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:33,079
A wild cat shouldn't be coming here.

10
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,920
I hope it doesn't come back.

11
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,400
Zhinian,

12
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:57,599
did you know I was coming,

13
00:01:57,959 --> 00:02:00,040
so you left a light on for me?

14
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,560
I know I'm in your heart.

15
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,239
Zhinian.

16
00:02:11,330 --> 00:02:12,479
Where did this wild cat come from?

17
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,360
Annoying!

18
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:25,080
Where did you go?

19
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:25,759
I...

20
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:27,960
Just walked around.

21
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,159
This is the harem.

22
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,800
You're an outside male wandering around.

23
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:33,520
If you're discovered,
I won't be able to save you.

24
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,080
You can't save me?

25
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,759
Then, why did you bring me in?

26
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,919
(If you weren't going
to be the top scholar,)

27
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:42,360
(who would bother coaxing you?)

28
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:43,960
Lu,

29
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,159
what do you mean?

30
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:49,560
If I didn't want Dowager Consort
to recommend you,

31
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:52,199
why would I come
all the way to the capital?

32
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,360
But the peach tree withered.

33
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:57,159
Dowager Consort is displeased.

34
00:02:59,199 --> 00:03:01,960
Duke Zhen and Duke Ding
are at each other's throats.

35
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,520
To deal with Duke Zhen,

36
00:03:04,530 --> 00:03:06,159
the Emperor is vigorously
supporting the Liu family.

37
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:08,000
You should just turn to the Liu family.

38
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:09,439
They need manpower.

39
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,759
You're from a sheltered home.

40
00:03:13,199 --> 00:03:14,639
How do you know all this?

41
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:16,360
Of course, it's because my last...

42
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:23,280
I heard it from Dowager Consort

43
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,599
a while ago.

44
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:30,400
I hope it's as you say.

45
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:32,599
Otherwise, never mind my future,

46
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:34,280
even my life will be lost here.

47
00:03:35,439 --> 00:03:37,199
Lu, why must you be so cowardly?

48
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,439
You are the man who
will be the top scholar.

49
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,280
Top scholar?

50
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,599
It's not that easy to
become the top scholar.

51
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,439
(So overcautious.)

52
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,919
(Looking all weak and useless.)

53
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:50,159
(How did he pass
the exams in my past life?)

54
00:03:56,599 --> 00:03:57,879
What happened to my hand?

55
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,719
What...

56
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:01,280
What did you touch?

57
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,960
What could I have touched?

58
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:06,639
Forget it.

59
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,080
Go get me some medicine.

60
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:10,800
Tomorrow, I still have to copy scriptures
for Dowager Consort.

61
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,000
Go.

62
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:28,740
(Letter to Lu Jianglin)

63
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,639
You are heartless to me.

64
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:38,439
Why did you come to find me
time and again

65
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,920
after entering the Cold Palace?

66
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:44,040
Could there really be a hidden reason
for you entering the palace?

67
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:46,079
Your Majesty,

68
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:47,959
while investigating Lu Jianglin,

69
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:51,079
we discovered these past letters
between him and Shen Zhinian.

70
00:04:51,079 --> 00:04:52,260
(Hand in hand beneath the moon,
together till white hair and frost)

71
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,800
What a display of deep affection,

72
00:04:54,850 --> 00:04:56,240
with such constant correspondence.

73
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,390
Your Majesty, your hand has
been itching all night without relief.

74
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,920
What exactly is wrong?

75
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,390
Should we summon the imperial physician
again to take a look?

76
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,800
Go to the Cold Palace.

77
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,800
Miss, I went to deliver
medicine to Xu Baoqin today.

78
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:30,319
The eunuch told me that Great General Xu
used a death-exemption medal

79
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,680
to get her out.

80
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:35,040
The Xu family's death-exemption medal?

81
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:38,160
(If I could also obtain
a death-exemption medal,)

82
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:39,519
(my maternal family and I)

83
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:41,160
(would escape the fate of my past life.)

84
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,199
Lord Jiang, you're here.

85
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:46,920
Lord Jiang.

86
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:50,040
Miss Shen, you said
an orchid has withered.

87
00:05:50,210 --> 00:05:51,199
I've come to take a look.

88
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:53,480
Thank you, Lord Jiang.

89
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,079
Lord Jiang, please come in.

90
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,800
Please look, sir.

91
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,680
These orchids need to see some sunlight.

92
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,879
The window is broken.

93
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:07,800
Be careful not to hurt your hand, sir...

94
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:13,519
I'll find someone to fix it later.

95
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:14,720
The night is cold.

96
00:06:14,730 --> 00:06:16,290
It won't do if the window won't close.

97
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,639
It's more than just the cold.

98
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:18,990
There are wild cats making trouble.

99
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,480
I'll go see the Empress.

100
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:24,680
I'll ask her to find
a way to get you out.

101
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,240
If that can really happen,

102
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:28,320
I thank you on behalf
of the Young Lady, Lord Jiang.

103
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,279
Handan,

104
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:30,920
don't trouble Lord Jiang.

105
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:33,079
Her Highness is unwell.

106
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:36,079
How can we trouble her
with such trivial matters?

107
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:41,800
Why do I have a rash on my hand?

108
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:47,560
The window might have grown mold.

109
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,959
You're having an allergic reaction.

110
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:50,879
You should go to the Imperial Hospital.

111
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:52,759
His Majesty has arrived!

112
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,959
Jiang Chen?

113
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,480
Why are you here too?

114
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:06,639
I came to see
the orchids Miss Shen planted.

115
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,879
Since when did you two become so close?

116
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,399
We aren't close at all.

117
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,879
I've always cherished
orchids like my own life.

118
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,959
I couldn't bear to see them ruined,

119
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,680
so I made a special trip.

120
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,839
What happened to your hand?

121
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,759
I'm not sure what happened.

122
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,360
I only stayed at
Miss Shen's for a while,

123
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:30,360
and a rash broke out for no reason.

124
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:33,800
The Cold Palace hasn't
been cared for in years.

125
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:35,399
There are many insects.

126
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,560
I must have been bitten.

127
00:07:37,279 --> 00:07:38,560
County Princess, you can't go in.

128
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:40,360
This is the Dowager Consort's token.

129
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,160
Step aside.

130
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:44,199
What are you afraid of?

131
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:46,199
If you're bold enough
to exchange love poems,

132
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,800
then write them in front of me.

133
00:07:47,810 --> 00:07:49,730
Write them a hundred times
if once isn't enough.

134
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:51,920
Your Majesty.

135
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,240
Your Majesty.

136
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:56,399
Long live Your Majesty.

137
00:07:56,839 --> 00:07:58,199
What are you doing here?

138
00:07:59,839 --> 00:08:01,279
I...

139
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,279
I know

140
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:05,000
my sister likes writing poems,

141
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,720
so I brought her brush and ink

142
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:08,519
to help her pass the time.

143
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,759
Bring them here.

144
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,480
Did I give you permission to rise?

145
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:44,190
(He has a red rash on his hand too.)

146
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:46,080
(He was also here last night.)

147
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:49,080
(It seems I wasn't
the only one here last night.)

148
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:51,559
(Every one of them is so bold.)

149
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,480
It seems this Cold Palace

150
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:54,970
is even livelier than Shanglin Garden.

151
00:08:55,559 --> 00:08:56,879
Since you all like it so much,

152
00:08:57,660 --> 00:08:58,600
you should all move in.

153
00:08:59,650 --> 00:09:00,559
I beg for forgiveness.

154
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:03,240
I'll never come here again.

155
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:05,120
All of you, dismissed.

156
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:08,679
I take my leave.

157
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,519
What should your punishment be

158
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,039
for plotting against me?

159
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,200
Oh?

160
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:28,039
What happened to your hand,
Your Majesty?

161
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:28,879
Stop pretending.

162
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:33,039
You sent me to
the Cold Palace for no reason.

163
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:34,879
Can't I even fix my own window

164
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,279
to hide from wild cats?

165
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,559
You're guarding against me?

166
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:40,200
You're not a wild cat.

167
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:41,919
You are a true dragon,

168
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,000
the Son of Heaven.

169
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,440
Even in the Cold Palace,

170
00:09:46,039 --> 00:09:47,519
your tongue is still as sharp as ever.

171
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,879
I'll use some mint water

172
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,080
to wipe your hand,

173
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,600
so your imperial hand feels better.

174
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:58,380
♪Faint rouge hides
the tenderness in the eyes♪

175
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:01,580
♪Every step is treacherous,
regardless of the world♪

176
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:05,460
♪Flowers wither easily,
but obsession remains♪

177
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,000
Shen Zhinian.

178
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:08,519
Yes?

179
00:10:09,190 --> 00:10:10,519
You're hiding something from me.

180
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:15,120
I'm hiding many things from you.

181
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,679
Which one are you asking about?

182
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,639
You certainly are bold.

183
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,559
In one's life,

184
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:22,879
how can one not tell a few lies?

185
00:10:23,159 --> 00:10:25,120
Lies can be
well-intentioned or malicious.

186
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,919
I have no malice toward you.

187
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,000
Only admiration.

188
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:32,159
I just want to win your favor.

189
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:36,279
You want to win my favor?

190
00:10:36,879 --> 00:10:37,440
Yes.

191
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,480
Every woman in the harem wants that.

192
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:40,919
But I

193
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,600
want it most.

194
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,720
Since you want my favor so badly,

195
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,559
I'll give you a chance.

196
00:10:54,039 --> 00:10:55,320
Before dawn,

197
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:59,480
write one hundred love poems.

198
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,620
And you'll let me
out of the Cold Palace?

199
00:11:02,639 --> 00:11:03,800
Depends on your performance.

200
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:06,919
Your Majesty,

201
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,279
I won't close the window tonight.

202
00:11:23,679 --> 00:11:25,279
What does His Majesty mean by this?

203
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,360
To keep out wild cats.

204
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,990
It's good that they nailed it shut.

205
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,159
I don't know where all these wild cats
in the Cold Palace come from.

206
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,000
They've been here three times already.

207
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,279
They even broke the windows.

208
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:35,570
Luckily, they didn't get
into your room, Young Lady.

209
00:11:35,679 --> 00:11:37,720
Those three "wild cats" who came by

210
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,720
were actually

211
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:39,440
His Majesty,

212
00:11:39,559 --> 00:11:40,399
Jiang Chen,

213
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,480
and Lu Jianglin.

214
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,550
They all had red rashes on their hands.

215
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,759
What?

216
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,559
Young Lady, you must be mistaken.

217
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,559
Why would Lord Jiang

218
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,000
climb over a wall?

219
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,679
Besides, the rash on his hand

220
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:54,399
might have happened during the day.

221
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:57,600
Didn't you smell the ointment

222
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,879
on Lord Jiang's palm?

223
00:11:59,279 --> 00:12:02,320
And judging by how severe the rash was,

224
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,399
it didn't look like it started today.

225
00:12:05,519 --> 00:12:07,840
To think a refined gentleman
would actually

226
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,279
resort to climbing walls.

227
00:12:09,590 --> 00:12:11,320
As expected,
not a single man is any good.

228
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,759
Never mind him for now.

229
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:14,720
Let's go back and prepare the ink.

230
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,200
The Emperor ordered me
to write a hundred poems.

231
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,190
I have to get them done quickly.

232
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,480
A hundred poems?

233
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,399
How can you finish that in one night?

234
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,990
If he wants a hundred,
he'll get a hundred.

235
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,380
He wants to make
things difficult for me,

236
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,780
so I'm going to show him I can do it.

237
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:25,279
Let's go.

238
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:30,440
Your Majesty,
I've brought all the anti-itch ointments

239
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,380
from the Imperial Hospital.

240
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:32,480
Let Lu itch to death.

241
00:12:32,759 --> 00:12:33,919
It's not just Lu Jianglin.

242
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,360
Jiang Chen also has a rash on his hands.

243
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,200
Well played, Shen Zhinian.

244
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:40,120
Seeing three men in a single night, huh?

245
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:43,200
Could it be that Jiang Chen
was also bewitched by her?

246
00:12:58,679 --> 00:12:59,879
(Could it be)

247
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,279
(that she coaxed him
the same way she coaxed me?)

248
00:13:03,919 --> 00:13:04,480
Your Majesty,

249
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,960
Lady Shen's hundred poems

250
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,679
are here.

251
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:08,700
(On the high cliff, strong wings rest.
The wind curls, the gaze is cold)

252
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:10,360
She finished so quickly?

253
00:13:13,340 --> 00:13:14,500
(Not playing with the common sparrows,
spreading wings toward the clouds)

254
00:13:22,470 --> 00:13:24,120
What a fine way to
express her ambitions.

255
00:13:24,759 --> 00:13:26,080
A whole hundred poems of it.

256
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,890
Did I even ask her to
express her ambitions?

257
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:48,240
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

258
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:55,200
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

259
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:59,200
♪If we don't meet♪

260
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:02,640
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

261
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:09,360
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

262
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:16,160
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

263
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:22,840
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

264
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:30,040
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

265
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:36,920
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

266
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:43,040
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

267
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:50,560
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

268
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:57,400
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

269
00:14:57,680 --> 00:15:04,120
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

